item.title: About me
item.author: bapt.hudyma95650@gmail.com (Baptiste Hudyma)
item.description: Hi ! My name is Baptiste Hudyma, I’m a robotic engineer way too curious about way too many subjects. From programming to wood crafting, from physics to video games, and events organization, In this blog/posts mashup/portfolio thingy, you will find details on some projects that I thought were interesting to share It will also serve as a written trace of some realizations, enabling me to take more time and more room to explain what the idea and processes behind those projects.
